What We Do

A Little Something For Everyone

Explore our Scratch Patch with 26 types of stones. Enjoy delicious coffee on our deck. We sell sterling silver jewellery and rocks from across Africa. Plenty of parking available.

The Scratch Patch at the Rockshop

At The Rockshop at Hartbeespoort, our tumble stone scratch patch is a magical adventure for kids.

With four cup sizes to choose from, little treasure hunters can dig through a rainbow of polished stones, filling their cups with their favourite finds.

Each unique tumble stone becomes a keepsake of wonder and curiosity.

Once filled, their special collection is carefully packed into a beautiful organza drawstring bag to take home — a pouch of memories, mystery, and sparkling dreams.

It’s more than just stones; it’s the joy of discovery, learning, and creating lasting moments with family.

We stock a wide range of bracelets in gemstones and stainless steel. As well as necklaces in stone and sterling silver set with stones. Our range changes often

Hartbeespoort Dam

Hartbeespoort is a popular tourist spot just outside Johannesburg, known for its scenic dam, mountains, and weekend getaways. A visit to The Rockshop at Harties is a must—browse beautiful crystals, fossils, and silver jewellery, enjoy great coffee on the deck, and let the kids play in the Scratch Patch.
